data.description: Welcome to this 4 bedroom 3 bath plus a loft newer build home in the highly desirable Heritage Lake community. Built in 2021 this home features luxury vinyl plank flooring. There is a formal dining space as well as a breakfast table area in the kitchen. The kitchen boasts quartz counters, a single basin sink, double ovens and a walk in pantry. There is a bedroom and bath downstairs. Upstairs is an open loft. The laundry room is upstairs and has a built in shelf. There is a Quiet Cool brand whole house fan. Tankless water heater. Solar on the home.The back yard is low maintenance. Walking distance to elementary school and park. Community features lake, pools, spa, splash park, sports courts, tot lots, trails, clubhouse and community activities. The home is move in ready, come check it out! Furniture is negotiable.
